snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Nili
snippet.description:
How to play Nili

War hero, she needs his combination to breathe on the surface of his devasted planet.
Nili has a great range with his gun and can burst fire. She can use his walljump to reload at a safety position.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
